metadata.description: Swadesh 100-item core vocabulary list with translations for 142 NLLB-supported languages
metadata.source: Compiled from Wiktionary, ASJP, and standard Swadesh references
metadata.expansion_note: Expanded from 40 to 142 languages. Original 40-language translations compiled from Wiktionary, ASJP, and standard Swadesh references. Additional translations compiled from published Swadesh lists, linguistic databases, and reference grammars. All expanded translations should be verified by native speakers before publication. Armenian (hye_Armn) removed due to systematic script corruption (Latin transliterations instead of native script). Tigrinya (tir_Ethi) corrected with verified Ge'ez script translations from Wiktionary and standard Tigrinya references.
metadata.verification: Cross-referenced against ASJP v20 (Wichmann et al. 2022). 132/141 languages matched via ISO 639-3 codes; 89 Latin-script languages achieved 88.9% average similarity. See swadesh_verification_report.json for details.
